<div class="theorem" id="theorem-NMLIC" acro="NMLIC" titletext="Nonsingular Matrices have Linearly Independent Columns">
<h5 class="theorem">
<span class="type">Theorem </span><span class="acro">NMLIC</span><span class="titletext"> Nonsingular Matrices have Linearly Independent Columns</span>
</h5>
<div class="statement"><p>Suppose that $A$ is a square matrix.  Then $A$ is nonsingular if and only if the columns of $A$ form a linearly independent set.</p></div>
<div class="proof"><a knowl="./knowls/proof.NMLIC.knowl">Proof</a></div>
